title: Erin Killeen | @etkfit unfiltered: reality checks, self worth, comparison
itunes:author: Brittany Lupton
description:
This weeks guest is bringing all of the inspiration to fuel your week with some good old this-or-that fun & all of the self worth gains. Erin Killeen, aka @etkfit, joins Britt to chat about having your own back, reality checks, how to quit comparing, gym confidence, mindset, leaving unhealthy relationships, training splits, support systems & so much more!
